<!-- ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê -->
<!-- üé¨ ANIMACIONES CON GSAP                                     -->
<!-- ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê -->
<script>
    import { gsap } from "gsap";

    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
        console.log("üíç Iniciando animaciones de portada...");

        // ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê ANIMACI√ìN DE ENTRADA - Texto cursiva ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê
        gsap.fromTo(
            ".font-great-vibes",
            { opacity: 0, y: -30 },
            { opacity: 1, y: 0, duration: 0.8, ease: "power2.out", delay: 0.3 }
        );

        // ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê ANIMACI√ìN DE ENTRADA - T√≠tulo principal ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê
        gsap.fromTo(
            "h1",
            { opacity: 0, scale: 0.8 },
            { opacity: 1, scale: 1, duration: 0.8, ease: "back.out(1.5)", delay: 0.6 }
        );

        // ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê ANIMACI√ìN DE L√çNEAS ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê
        gsap.fromTo(
            ".h-\\[2px\\]",
            { width: 0, opacity: 0 },
            { width: "100%", opacity: 1, duration: 0.8, ease: "power2.out", delay: 0.9, stagger: 0.2 }
        );

        // ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê ANIMACI√ìN DE FECHA ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê
        gsap.fromTo(
            ".tracking-wide",
            { opacity: 0 },
            { opacity: 1, duration: 0.6, ease: "power2.out", delay: 1.2 }
        );

        // ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê BOT√ìN INGRESAR CON FUNCIONALIDAD ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê
        const btnIngresar = document.getElementById('btn-ingresar');
        const portada = document.getElementById('portada-bienvenida');

        // Animaci√≥n de entrada del bot√≥n
        gsap.fromTo(
            "#btn-ingresar",
            { opacity: 0, y: 30, scale: 0.9 },
            { opacity: 1, y: 0, scale: 1, duration: 0.6, ease: "back.out(1.5)", delay: 1.5 }
        );

        btnIngresar?.addEventListener('click', () => {
            console.log("üö™ Cerrando portada...");
            
            // Animaci√≥n de salida suave
            gsap.to(portada, {
                opacity: 0,
                scale: 0.95,
                duration: 0.6,
                ease: "power2.inOut",
                onComplete: () => {
                    portada?.remove();
                    // Hacer scroll suave al inicio
                    window.scrollTo({ top: 0, behavior: 'smooth' });
                    console.log("‚úÖ Portada cerrada");
                }
            });
        });

        console.log("‚ú® Animaciones de portada completadas!");
    });
</script>

<style>
    /* Fuentes personalizadas */
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Great+Vibes&display=swap');

    .font-great-vibes {
        font-family: 'Great Vibes', cursive;
    }

    /* Prevenir scroll mientras est√° la portada */
    body:has(#portada-bienvenida) {
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    /* Optimizaci√≥n de rendimiento */
    #btn-ingresar {
        backface-visibility: hidden;
        -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
    }
</style>